@startuml
actor Client
participant "Rails API (Auth Controller)" as AuthController
participant "Rails API (Application Controller)" as ApplicationController
participant "Database" as DB

== 用户注册/登录 ==
Client -> AuthController : 1. POST /signup 或 /login (username, password)
AuthController -> DB : 2. 查询/创建用户
alt 注册成功
    DB --> AuthController : 3. 用户数据 (已保存/创建)
    AuthController --> Client : 4. 返回 201 Created / 200 OK
else 登录成功
    DB --> AuthController : 3. 用户数据 (已验证)
    AuthController -> AuthController : 4. 生成 JWT (包含用户ID等)
    AuthController --> Client : 5. 返回 200 OK, { "jwt": "eyJ...", "user": {...} }
else 注册/登录失败
    AuthController --> Client : 4. 返回 401 Unauthorized / 422 Unprocessable Entity
end

== 后续受保护的 API 请求 ==
Client -> ApplicationController : 1. GET /users/profile (Header: Authorization: Bearer eyJ...)
ApplicationController -> ApplicationController : 2. 验证 JWT
alt JWT 有效
    ApplicationController -> DB : 3. 获取请求数据
    DB --> ApplicationController : 4. 数据
    ApplicationController --> Client : 5. 返回 200 OK, { "data": {...} }
else JWT 无效/过期
    ApplicationController --> Client : 3. 返回 401 Unauthorized
end
@enduml